c1=A.a(["e-Rupee is India's CBDC issued by RBI \u2014 two tiers: wholesale (e\u20b9-W) and retail (e\u20b9-R)","Wholesale pilot with 9 banks for interbank settlements","Retail version supports offline transactions and UPI interoperability","Programmable money enables targeted subsidies (e.g., fertilizer to farmers)","Complements physical currency \u2014 does not replace cash"],b8)
